 {{t+|vi|cà chua}}\n* Walloon: {{t+|wa|tomate|f}}\n* Yakut: {{t|sah|помидор}}, {{t|sah|томат}}\n* Yoruba: {{t|yo|tòmátì}}\n* Zazaki: {{t|zza|şamık|f}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n{{trans-top|fruit}}\n* Abkhaz: {{t|ab|апаҭырџьан}}, {{t|ab|атома́т}}\n* Afrikaans: {{t|af|tamatie}}\n* Albanian: {{t+|sq|domate}}, {{t+|sq|mollatartë}}\n* Amharic: {{t|am|ቲማቲም}}\n* Arabic: {{t|ar|بَنْدُورَة|f}}, {{t|ar|طَمَاطِم|m}}\n*: Egyptian Arabic: {{t|arz|قوطة|f|tr=ʔūṭa}} {{qualifier|collective}}, {{t|arz|قوطاية|f|tr=ʔuṭāya}} (''[[singulative]]''); {{t|arz|طماطم|m|tr=ṭamāṭem}} {{qualifier|collective}}, {{t|arz|طمطماية|f|tr=ṭamaṭmāya}} (''[[singulative]]'')\n*: Moroccan Arabic: {{t|ary|ماطيشة|f|tr=maṭīša}}\n*: South Levantine Arabic: {{t|ajp|بندورة|tr=bandōra}}\n* Aramaic:\n*: Assyrian Neo-Aramaic: {{t|aii|ܛܵܡܵܛܵܐ|tr=ṭamaṭa|m}}\n*: Lishana Deni: {{t|lsd|בנגׄאנא סמוקתא|tr=banjāna smuqta|f}}, {{t|lsd|באגׄאנא סמוקא|tr=bājāna smoqa|m}}\n* Armenian: {{t+|hy|լոլիկ}}, {{t+|hy|պոմիդոր}}\n* Aromanian: {{t|rup|tumatã|f}}\n* Assamese: {{t|as|বিলাহী}}\n* Asturian: {{t+|ast|tomate|m}}, {{t+|ast|tomate|m}}\n* Azerbaijani: {{t+|az|pomidor}}, {{t|az|rus badımcanı}} {{qualifier|obsolete}}\n* Bangi: {{t|bni|tomati}}\n* Banjarese: {{t|bjn|balinjan}}, {{t|bjn|bulinjan}}\n* Bashkir: {{t|ba|помидор}}\n* Belarusian: {{t|be|памідо́р|m}}, {{t|be|тама́т|m}}\n* Bengali: {{t+|bn|বিলাতী বেগুন}}, {{t+|bn|টমেটো}}\n* Bouyei: {{t|pcc|legridt}}\n* Breton: [[tomatez]] {{qualifier|collective}} {{t+|br|tomatezenn|f}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t+|bg|дома́т|m}}\n* Burmese: {{t|my|ခရမ်းချင်သီး}}, {{t+|my|ခရမ်းချဉ်}}, {{t+|my|မြေပုံသီး}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|tomàquet|m}}\n* Chechen: {{t|ce|адамат}}, {{t|ce|бадарж}}, {{t|ce|помидор}}, {{t|ce|томат}}, {{t|ce|помдор}}\n* Cherokee: {{t|chr|ᏔᎹᏟ}}, {{t|chr|ᏓᎹᏟ}}\n* Chichewa: {{t|ny|phwetekere}}, {{t|ny|matimati}}, {{t|ny|tomato}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Cantonese: {{t|yue|番茄|tr=faan1 ke4-2}}\n*: Dungan: {{t|dng|сызы}}, {{t|dng|памдар}}\n*: Eastern Min: {{t|cdo|番柿|tr=huăng-kê}}\n*: Gan: {{t|gan|番茄}}\n*: Hakka: {{t|hak|番茄|tr=fân-khiò}}\n*: Hokkien: {{t+|nan-hbl|柑仔蜜|tr=kam-á-bi̍t}}, {{t|nan-hbl|柑仔得|tr=kam-á-tit, kam-á-te}}, {{t|nan-hbl|臭柿仔|tr=chhàu-khī-á}}, {{t|nan-hbl|番茄|tr=hoan-kiô}}, {{t|nan-hbl|tho͘-má-to͘h}}\n*: Jin: {{t|cjy|西紅柿}}, {{t|cjy|西番柿}}\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|西紅柿}}, {{t+|cmn|番茄}}, {{t+|cmn|柿子}} {{q|dialectal}}\n*: Northern Min: {{t|mnp|番柿}}\n*: Wu: {{t|wuu|番茄}}\n*: Xiang: {{t|hsn|番茄}}, {{t|hsn|西紅柿}}\n* Chuvash: {{t|cv|помидор}}\n* Circassian:\n*: East Circassian: {{t+|kbd|бэдрэжан}}\n*: West Circassian: {{t|ady|цугу}}\n* Cornish: {{t|kw|aval kerensa|m}}\n* Crimean Tatar: {{t|crh|domatis}}, {{t|crh|pamidor}}\n* Czech: {{t+|cs|rajče|n}}, {{t|cs|rajské jablíčko|n}}\n* Danish: {{t+|da|tomat|c}}\n* Dusun:\n*: Central Dusun: {{t|dtp|tamatus}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|tomaat|f}}\n* Elfdalian: {{t|ovd|tomat|m}}\n* Esperanto: {{t+|eo|tomato}}\n* Estonian: {{t+|et|tomat}}\n* Faroese: {{t|fo|tomat|f}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|tomaatti}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|tomate|f}}\n* Frisian:\n*: North Frisian: {{t|frr|Tomaat|f}} {{q|Sylt}}, {{t|frr|toomaot|f}} {{q|Halligen}}\n*: Saterland Frisian: {{t|stq|Tomoate|f}}\n*: West Frisian: {{t|fy|tomaat|c}}\n* Gagauz: {{t|gag|tomat}}\n* Galician: {{t+|gl|tomate|m}}\n* Georgian: {{t|ka|პამიდორი}}, {{t|ka|ტომატი}}, {{t+|ka|პომიდორი}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Tomate|f}}, {{t+|de|Paradeiser|m}} {{q|Austria}}\n* Greek: {{t+|el|ντομάτα|f}}\n* Greenlandic: {{t|kl|tomati}}\n* Guarani:\n*: Paraguayan Guarani: {{t-check|gug|tomate}}\n* Gujarati: {{t|gu|ટમેટું}}\n* Haitian Creole: {{t|ht|tomat}}\n* Hawaiian: {{t|haw|ʻōhiʻa haole}}, {{t|haw|ʻōhiʻa lomi}}, {{t|haw|komako}}\n* Hebrew: {{t+|he|עַגְבָנִיָּה|f|tr=agvaniyá}}, {{t|he|בַּדּוּרָה|f|tr=badura}} {{qualifier|archaic}}\n* Hindi: {{t+|hi|टमाटर|m}}, {{t+|hi|विलायती|m|tr=vilāyatī}}\n* Hungarian: {{t+|hu|paradicsom}}\n* Hunsrik: {{t|hrx|Tomatt|f}}\n* Icelandic: {{t+|is|tómatur|m}}, {{t+|is|tómati|m}} {{qualifier|rare}}, {{t|is|rauðaldin|n}} {{qualifier|rare}}\n* Ido: {{t+|io|tomato}}\n* Indonesian: {{t+|id|tomat}}\n*